&lt;li&gt;Gather &amp;amp; analyze intelligence about the market, identifying trends about key prospects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in regular planning, strategy, and training meetings with our horizontal industry team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model good sales practices and maintain accurate opportunity records&lt;/li&gt;
